  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/17ea5b3135880da5c3f61df675014181.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/17ea5b3135880da5c3f61df675014181.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Teamwork is essential. In <i>Egg Raiders</i>, you and your team must rely on strategy, distraction, and quick reflexes to outwit the monsters and survive. Every decision matters, as one misstep could cost the entire team.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/7cbc1d7f7bb821bf0770d33607f669ba.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/7cbc1d7f7bb821bf0770d33607f669ba.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The monsters in <i>Egg Raiders</i> aren’t just mindless creatures—they’re driven by instinct to protect their territory from intruders. Once they’ve detected you, they will stop at nothing to track you down. Your team must remain vigilant, using every tool at your disposal to avoid their relentless pursuit.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/497c314c56a4c3d3c42904e98af959b1.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/497c314c56a4c3d3c42904e98af959b1.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time is of the essence. You have three in-game days to loot, survive, and make as much money as possible. The clock is ticking, and each decision—whether to stay longer for more loot or escape safely—can make or break your progress.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/d8fd3521d1a0974b78f6cf86dbaec016.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/d8fd3521d1a0974b78f6cf86dbaec016.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you stay for one more heist to grab that valuable item, or escape now with what you have? The deeper you venture and the longer you stay, the greater the rewards—but also the greater the risk. Greed could lead to riches, or it could spell your doom.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/17ea5b3135880da5c3f61df675014181.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/17ea5b3135880da5c3f61df675014181.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Teamwork is essential. In <i>Egg Raiders</i>, you and your team must rely on strategy, distraction, and quick reflexes to outwit the monsters and survive. Every decision matters, as one misstep could cost the entire team.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/7cbc1d7f7bb821bf0770d33607f669ba.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/7cbc1d7f7bb821bf0770d33607f669ba.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline p